    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DoValue 在 Elliott 交易中达成接近 4.5 亿欧元的银行融资协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/italian-debt-servicer-dovalue-nears-450-million-financing-for-elliott-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利金融服务专业公司 DoValue SpA 即将与多家银行达成协议，提供约 4.5 亿欧元（合 4.89 亿美元）的信贷额度，这是完成与 Elliott Investment Management 旗下 Gardant SpA 服务部门合并的关键一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/italian-debt-servicer-dovalue-nears-450-million-financing-for-elliott-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 15:19:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对加拿大降息的押注为落后银行带来希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/bets-on-canada-rate-cut-hold-out-hope-for-underperforming-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多伦多湾街上下的投资者越来越多地押注加拿大六月降息，这可能会提振加拿大长期低迷的银行股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/bets-on-canada-rate-cut-hold-out-hope-for-underperforming-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 14:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球任职时间最长的央行行长将在罗马尼亚连任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/world-s-longest-serving-central-bank-chief-to-get-new-term-in-romania</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界上任职时间最长的央行行长罗马尼亚穆古尔·伊萨雷斯库 (Mugur Isarescu) 即将获得新的五年任期确认，议员们寻求在 6 月底之前就延长任期进行投票。]]></description>
